---
title: Smart Togarashi Shrimp and Slaw Bowls with Edamame and Guacamole
description: Bright and flavourful; this bowl is packed with edamame, spiced sesame shrimp, zippy slaw, cooling lime crema and finished with a dollop of guacamole!

